Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Sport and tax avoidance
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xl0p
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 14 Jul 1985
Top sports players who leave home to avoid paying taxes. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.